pageTitle: Itinerary for Wednesday, October 12, 2016 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Wednesday, October 12, 2016:

Ottawa, Ontario

7:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will host a working dinner for the Prime Minister of the French Republic, His Excellency Manuel Valls.

Notes for media:

  • Closed to media
